_sText:
This map is the remastered version of trikz_versus which was posted months ago.

All the levels were retextured with shining textures and improved to do the map as fast as possible.

There are only 4 spawns (2 per team).

This map was made for sv_airaccelerate 10 and can be easily used as tournament map.

The map is composed of many levels which are 1 runboost + jump, 4 stackboosts, 4 longjumps, 1 flashboost, 1 little xc, 1 surf + bhop (made for aa10), 1 skyjump and 2 little bhops.


Good Luck & Have Fun :D
